167353.「行きはよいよい 帰りは怖い……。:
The way there is good, the way back is
scary...

167354.「邪気をはろうた あざやかな手並み\n ……よろしおすなぁ。:
The brilliant hand that has removed the evil
spirits....I love it.

167355.「せやけど 背中には 注意しいや。\n 亡者どもは 常に背後から 忍び寄るんやか:
But watch your back. The walkers are always
sneaking up behind you.

167356.「ウチは 天地雷鳴士の陰の分家\n ……陰衆の頭領 ヨイ いいます。:
My name is Yoi, the leader of the Yin branch
of the druid family...the Yinshu.

167357.「あんたが 陽衆の新人はんやね。 \n 能天気女に たぶらかされはって\n かわ:
You must be the newcomer to the Yang Clan. You
poor thing, being played by a no-nonsense
woman.

167358.「ウチら陰衆は 呪術の名手……。\n 天地雷鳴士として 強うなりたいんなら\n:
We, the Inshu, are masters of witchcraft... If
you want to become stronger as a druid, you
can come to us anytime.

167360.「もしも これからも 陽衆を名乗るんなら\n せいぜい背中には 気ぃつけなはれ。:
If you are going to call yourself Yang Clan
from now on, watch your back at the very
least.
